 &reftitle.required;


  This extension requires libsodium
  â‰¥ 1.0.8.





 &reftitle.install;


  As of PHP 7.2.0 this extension is bundled with PHP. For older PHP versions
  this extension is available via PECL.




  Linux Systems


   In order to use this extension you must compile PHP with sodium support by
   using the --with-sodium[=DIR] configure
   option.





  Windows


   In order to use this extension you have to add
   extension=php_sodium.dll to &php.ini;.





  Installation via PECL


   &pecl.info;
   &url.pecl.package;libsodium







